1
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:42,040
Karma entangles, bonds hard to sever

2
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:45,799
The hairpin locks memories, dreams unreturned

3
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,640
Zhongzhou Censor Zhao Heng betrayed his country for glory

4
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:51,480
Selling the map of the frontier iron mines

5
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,159
We are ordered to raid the house

6
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,400
My name is Zhao Yun

7
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,040
Late one night in the 22nd year of Qingde

8
00:01:58,799 --> 00:01:59,959
The gates of the Zhao residence

9
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:01,680
Were kicked open by a group of masked assassins

10
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,680
Run, Miss

11
00:02:02,799 --> 00:02:03,280
That night

12
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:03,760
Hurry

13
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,040
All 103 members of the Zhao household

14
00:02:06,319 --> 00:02:07,319
Were killed

15
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,080
Get down, Miss

16
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,599
Only I survived by luck

17
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,199
Miss, hide yourself well

18
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:11,960
Don't make a sound

19
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,199
The Manor Lord said

20
00:02:21,639 --> 00:02:22,439
Slaughter the entire Zhao family

21
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,000
Nine Thousand Years will reward us

22
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,120
Yes

23
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:32,560
Rumors outside say my father, Zhao Heng,

24
00:02:33,039 --> 00:02:34,599
Had his family wiped out for treason

25
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:36,960
But I knew Father too well

26
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,680
He was loyal

27
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,199
And an honest official

28
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,759
He would never betray the court

29
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,840
Someone in court must have wanted to eliminate the Zhao family

30
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,360
And deliberately fabricated charges against Father

31
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:50,680
Since the day the Zhao family was massacred

32
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,680
I have thought every day

33
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:54,840
About finding that white mask

34
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:56,439
Finally

35
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,960
Fate let me meet them again

36
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:01,560
You want to die?

37
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,520
Stop

38
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:04,400
Are you okay, little girl?

39
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,439
Get up

40
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,560
Where are your parents?

41
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:14,719
Where is the rest of your family?

42
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,639
The Manor Lord mistook me for an orphan

43
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:22,240
And decided to take me back to the villa to accompany his daughter

44
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,360
He even named me Xiaobai

45
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,080
This name

46
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:28,240
Became a seed buried in my heart

47
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,280
A seed of revenge

48
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,080
Now

49
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:34,159
The revenge plan I have brewed for years in hiding

50
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,000
Can finally unfold

51
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,960
To those who killed my Zhao family

52
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:41,400
I will settle the blood debts of the past

53
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,599
My name is Huang Cui

54
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:47,560
Sister

55
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,400
Ever since my brother Yu'er

56
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,120
Went missing on my birthday

57
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,800
Haven't seen him

58
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,439
He vanished like a stone in the sea

59
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,159
Never to be heard from again

60
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,000
I asked around everywhere

61
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:57,360
I heard

62
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,520
He might be at the All-Knowing Villa

63
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,439
So I racked my brains

64
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:05,000
And found a way to infiltrate the villa

65
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,519
To find clues

66
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,839
I started as the lowest servant

67
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,439
And climbed step by step to the position of housekeeper

68
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:31,360
Behind the seeming smoothness

69
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,839
Someone was actually helping in secret

70
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:36,000
Housekeeper Huang

71
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:40,920
Housekeeper Huang is increasingly valued by the Manor Lord now

72
00:04:41,759 --> 00:04:42,959
Our connection from the marketplace

73
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,519
Can we continue it?

74
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,519
When I found news about Yu'er

75
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,079
He was already gone

76
00:04:55,199 --> 00:04:56,199
Xiaobai told me

77
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,560
That years ago, Yu'er

78
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:00,319
Was sold by the Manor Lord

79
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:02,480
To the powerful Sixth Lord as a scapegoat

80
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,519
Even his corpse could not be found

81
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,560
Do you want to avenge your brother?

82
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,000
For those who died in the All-Knowing Villa

83
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,439
Avenge all the innocent ghosts?

84
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:16,600
I do

85
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,319
I heard

86
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,639
I look like the Young Mistress

87
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:22,360
So I used this

88
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,360
To catch the Manor Lord's eye

89
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:25,680
Father

90
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:37,759
Say it again

91
00:05:40,879 --> 00:05:41,639
Father

92
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:42,839
Good

93
00:05:44,439 --> 00:05:45,240
From then on

94
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,439
I became the substitute for the villa's daughter

95
00:06:05,959 --> 00:06:07,040
My name is Ruan Lian.

96
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:08,800
You can also call me Si Niang.

97
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,360
At Fengqi Courtyard,

98
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,319
I was the most famous courtesan in the capital.

99
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:16,399
But I fell in love with a lowly constable.

100
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:18,439
Si Niang, you've finally arrived.

101
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:21,199
Thank you, Sixth Lord, for recommending me.

102
00:06:21,319 --> 00:06:22,759
Si Niang, please.

103
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,680
All right.

104
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,560
After tonight's All-Knowing Night Banquet,

105
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,120
I will have the money to redeem myself.

106
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:28,639
Wait for me.

107
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,160
We made a promise.

108
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,439
To save enough money together,

109
00:06:34,439 --> 00:06:35,439
for my redemption,

110
00:06:35,439 --> 00:06:36,560
and fly far away.

111
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:41,240
Drink up!

112
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,680
The Manor Lord used a thousand taels of silver as bait,

113
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:55,199
inviting me to dance at the All-Knowing Villa.

114
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,120
For the sake of my freedom,

115
00:07:00,879 --> 00:07:02,800
I readily believed the Manor Lord's lies,

116
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,839
and personally destroyed my own freedom.

117
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:10,639
My lover was killed by Zhang Shan.

118
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:13,839
I was forever separated from my beloved.

119
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:16,360
So I spent my days,

120
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:19,439
drowning myself in a drunken stupor.

121
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,879
I even got used to that life.

122
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,120
Until she appeared.

123
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,519
If you want to escape, I can help you.

124
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,560
Isn't a life of luxury good enough?

125
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:44,759
Why would I want to escape?

126
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,879
If you don't escape,

127
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,120
then make those who hurt you,

128
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:52,319
pay the price.

129
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,839
My name is Xu Qingqing.

130
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,279
I am the only daughter of the All-Knowing Villa.

131
00:08:05,199 --> 00:08:08,040
But my birth was a scandal,

132
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,600
too shameful to mention in the Villa.

133
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:11,959
To cover up my mother's shame,

134
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,199
my grandfather made his trusted accountant,

135
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,240
marry into the Villa,

136
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:17,680
and take my mother's surname.

137
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,040
Because of the birthmark on my face,

138
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,720
they never let me see guests since childhood,

139
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,920
and locked me in the West Courtyard.

140
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:28,199
After my grandfather passed away,

141
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,600
he not only killed my mother,

142
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:32,399
but also took everything that was hers.

143
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,159
To soothe his remaining shred of humanity,

144
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,759
he dug a secret tunnel in the Villa,

145
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:39,720
and hypocritically set up a shrine for my mother.

146
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,279
To avenge my mother,

147
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:45,559
I feigned madness every day, waiting for a chance.

148
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,720
Until he locked me in the ancestral hall.

149
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,440
Afterwards,

150
00:08:50,279 --> 00:08:51,519
I met them.

151
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,360
Hatred brought us together.

152
00:08:58,879 --> 00:09:00,320
We plotted in secret,

153
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:03,840
deciding to pay tribute to the spirits at the All-Knowing Night Banquet.

154
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,000
How did it go?

155
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,120
Did you get the item?

156
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,440
All things in the world are empty.

157
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:45,919
Only karma is not.

158
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:47,720
This ending,

159
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,519
is also fate.

160
00:10:13,919 --> 00:10:15,679
The Summer Solstice brings the All-Knowing Night,

161
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,679
with all things renewed, we await your arrival.

162
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:21,240
Tonight, the All-Knowing Night Banquet opens once more.

163
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:24,399
We look forward to your presence.
